2058-2064 West 6th Street, between Aves. T. and U. The gabled house (No. 2064), stood originally at the N.W:. corner of Neck Road and Van Sicklen Street, upon the site of which is now P.S. 95. W. Donnelly was the owner
in 1873, and one Bergen in 1915.
August 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
